OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome brightness at first in the
OL,6,Feast. Otherwise, cloudy with outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain, heavy at times. Becoming
OL,8,Fdrier towards the west coast in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FVariable cloud and some sunny
OL,12,Fthen clear spells for the Western
OL,13,FIsles. Otherwise cloudy with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain, these heavy and thundery at
OL,15,Ftimes. Rain largely clearing east by
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,176,160,301,260,100,100
