OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F175A1783657171
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAny overnight rain soon
OL,6,Fclearing east. Otherwise cooler and
OL,7,Fmainly cloudy with some patchy light
OL,8,Fdrizzle possible, but west coast
OL,9,Fbrightening up with some warm sunshine
OL,10,Fbreaking out.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA dry
OL,13,Ffew days with some sunshine at times,
OL,14,Fespecially Monday. Very warm in the
OL,15,Fwest with the best of the sunshine,
OL,16,Fcloudier at times in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
